		<content type="html" xml:space="preserve" xml:base="https://www.burgershot.gg/showthread.php?tid=409"><![CDATA[<span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size">An ASI which will automatically organize chat logs for you.</span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size">Rather than just creating a chatlog.txt file, the client will create the file with date and time as name (<span style="color: #24292e;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="font-weight: bold;" class="mycode_b">year-month-day hour.minutes.seconds.txt</span>)</span></span>, on a folder called "Chatlogs" which will be located on your <span style="color: #24292e;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size">GTA San Andreas User Files\SAMP folder.</span></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="color: #24292e;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size">Supported versions: 0.3.7-R1, 0.3.7-R2, 0.3.7-R3 and 0.3.DL</span></span></span><br />
<br />
<span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size"><span style="color: #24292e;" class="mycode_color"><span style="font-size: small;" class="mycode_size">Download: <a href="https://github.com/BrunoBM16/samp-chatlog-organizer/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="mycode_url">here</a></span></span></span><br />
